<i>seperti Paul McCartney, Bruce Springsteen,</i>
<i>Stevie Wonder, Barbra Streisand,</i>

24
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:39,696
<i>Elton John, Fleetwood Mac,</i>
<i>Lionel Richie, dan lainnya.</i>

25
00:04:39,780 --> 00:04:40,906
<i>Selama 30 tahun,</i>

26
